{"tid":1447102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民頭盔日","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:28.000Z","uid":266683,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0812377b350165050ef1ed77fa7fc6659c47b601","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"和理非進場時間<br />\n經過今日既警犬行動<br />\n已導致好多市民不必要既嚴重受傷<br />\n建議文宣搞一個全民頭盔日<br />\n我知大家都可能要搵食 手停口停 長期罷工成本高<br />\n但係你返工放工出去食飯個陣 可以帶個頭盔 有罩既上埋罩 冇就口罩<br />\n呢個已經係和理非最低消費又做到既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目的係：<br />\n抗議警犬濫權！<br />\n市民安全因警犬使用暴力已不再受到任何保障！<br />\n提醒大家呢個社會到底發生緊咩事！<br />\n支持前線既努力同犧牲！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以諗下，二百萬人出街返工都帶住頭盔口罩<br />\n會係一個點樣既視覺效果！<br />\n同時話比外界同遊客聽，香港唔係一個安全既地方，出街食個飯都隨時會被拘捕、中彈，遊客仲敢黎嗎？外國記者會點報導？<br />\n仲有就係，愈多人有gear，前線就愈安全！當大量人都有呢啲裝備，就算行街搜到已經唔代表啲咩，就算和理非而家都需要呢啲裝備保護自己，因為警犬已經痴左線！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b34d0b13cd17a7f438b8d242e5218f3c5dc1b64","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:04.000Z","msg":"自推 大家比意見"},{"pid":"1f81b56953ee21738250e1fbb0c568eea262f859","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"自推 大家比意見"},{"pid":"c2d54b4d5b209993b248605a11bd03e5c3cc9f18","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"自推 大家比意見"},{"pid":"2633e63037e27486fda271ca5a67f3d96707467e","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"自推 大家比意見"},{"pid":"66dd51dae34d166960757efeb07c98e146db2b0f","tid":1447102,"uid":45035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"從今日起 大家都要變勇武"},{"pid":"f5ce0b4dedc10591cd95848df6c3a9d9eaffee77","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66dd51dae34d166960757efeb07c98e146db2b0f","tid":1447102,"uid":45035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"從今日起 大家都要變勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"頭盔豬咀已經唔係勇武專利<br />\n和理非都要升級！"},{"pid":"edb989264b24a456fdb660b54313bf250c6d546e","tid":1447102,"uid":4931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"地鐵站已經有大量 神經毒素，地鐵大定要帶防毒面罩"},{"pid":"e918de8ee9b5c455d1499efa117815fd79443800","tid":1447102,"uid":11043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07337bfa4c13198ef186642152d307207fb7d103","tid":1447102,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a25bc6dee33201c2bc02c522c905fd52d7b911","tid":1447102,"uid":13959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65eae38598993fddde1a06a946dc47ab7973e5de","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edb989264b24a456fdb660b54313bf250c6d546e","tid":1447102,"uid":4931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"地鐵站已經有大量 神經毒素，地鐵大定要帶防毒面罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"提醒藍絲，地鐵站有大量催淚氣<br />\n唔知會唔會有殘留物"},{"pid":"1ec1b666cd691163fa6ab205cdbe8b447c7d4904","tid":1447102,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"f6f443f94ad032b5ff412aa18936fcb394653659","tid":1447102,"uid"